Product Name: Ambipur Car Air Freshener - Vanilla Bouquet, 7.5 ml Pouch
Product Description: Do you sometimes find that your car has an annoying persistent odour? OR do you often notice other passengers in your car being irritated with smells? Well this is more common an issue then you would think, particularly in the summer and monsoon seasons!
